<p>While Akshay leads the show, he is joined by an impressive ensemble cast, including Paresh Rawal, Tabu, Wamiqa Gabbi, Mithila Palkar, Jisshu&nbsp;Sengupta, Manoj Joshi, and Rajpal Yadav. Helmed by <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/priyadarshan-wants-to-save-rajpal-yadav-says-poor-guy-erred-due-to-less-education-i-knew-about-his-problem-1400737">Priyadarshan</a>, the film is produced by Shobha Kapoor, Ektaa R Kapoor, and Akshay Kumar.</p>

<p><strong>Akshay Kumar&rsquo;s work front</strong></p>

<p>It&rsquo;s a known fact that Akshay&nbsp;delivers multiple movies in a year. Hence, after Bhooth Bangla, he will be seen in another family entertainer, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/welcome-to-the-jungle-akshay-kumar-suniel-shetty-raveena-tandons-film-to-hit-cinemas-on-june-26-1400237">Welcome to the Jungle</a>. The Ahmed Khan directorial is a multi-starrer movie featuring Suniel Shetty, Jackie Shroff, Raveena Tandon, Disha Patani, Jacqueline Fernandez, Arshad Warsi, Paresh Rawal, Rajpal Yadav, Johnny Lever, Aftab Shivdasani, Lara Dutta, Shreyas Talpade, and Tusshar Kapoor.</p>

