<p><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/sonu-sood-gurmeet-choudhary-offer-financial-help-to-rajpal-yadav-urge-producers-to-come-forward-1400619">Rajpal Yadav</a> and filmmaker <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/priyadarshan-lauds-his-disciple-aditya-dhar-for-dhurandhars-mega-success-latter-bows-down-to-his-master-1399761">Priyadarshan</a> have collaborated in multiple movies together. Hence, over the past decades, they have created a special bond with each other. Looking at Yadav&nbsp;struggling&nbsp;with finances and spending his days behind bars, the director has decided to lend a helping hand to the actor. While talking to Mid-Day, the <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/paresh-rawal-on-hera-pheri-3-controversy-with-akshay-kumar-and-makers-the-film-without-babu-rao-will-be-a-disaster-1400275">Hera Pheri</a> helmer stated that he has known the actor for 20 years.</p>

