<p>Apparently, the <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/bhooth-bangla-new-release-date-akshay-kumar-starrer-prepones-premiere-to-april-10-2026-1400547">Bhooth Bangla</a> maker knew about the Bhool Bhulaiyaa actor&rsquo;s problem. Hence, he kept signing Rajpal for every film and even pushed him in ad films too. &ldquo;The poor guy made a blunder because of his poor education. Rajpal is a good soul,&rdquo; expressed the ace Indian filmmaker.</p>

<p>The first time they worked together was in the 2000 film Jungle. Priyadarshan was surprised by his performance. Their first film together was Malamaal Weekly, and after that, Rajpal starred in most of his films. According to reports, Priyadarshan&rsquo;s next movie is a comic caper starring Pankaj Tripathi and Rajpal Yadav.</p>

