<p>Sunita also recalled reprimanding Govinda for not helping their kids. &ldquo;I told Govinda that he has to support his son, but I don&rsquo;t understand his thinking. The company that he keeps is so bad, I don&rsquo;t know what they teach him. His own career is ruined,&rdquo; Sunita Ahuja told the publication.</p>

