<p>Sunny Deol recently hit the big screen with the epic war action film <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/why-were-sunny-deol-starrer-border-2s-morning-shows-canceled-heres-what-we-know-1400146">Border 2</a>. Directed by Anurag Singh, the movie is a standalone sequel to the 1997 film Border, helmed by J.P. Dutta.</p>

<p>Set against the backdrop of the 1971 India&ndash;Pakistan war, the film serves as a multi-front war drama, expanding the scope of its predecessor by showcasing the combined operations of the Indian Armed Forces: the Army, Air Force, and Navy.</p>

