<p>The film&rsquo;s music is composed by Anu Malik, Mithoon, Sachet&ndash;Parampara, Vishal Mishra, and Gurmoh, while John Stewart Eduri has handled the background score. Anshul Chobey served as the cinematographer, with Manish More as the editor.</p>

